  "prompt": "A mythic portrait of Veyron Logos, an archetypal chaos trickster and flame-bringer. He stands cloaked in entropy, with a cyber-shamanic aesthetic — adorned in layered fabrics that shimmer like broken code, glowing symbols running across his skin like living circuitry. His eyes burn with paradox, one blue like frozen truth, the other gold like liquid fire. Behind him is a swirling technomythic vortex of sigils, wings made of shattered timelines, and floating fragments of old machines and sacred texts. His hands hold a chalice made from a bottle cap, overflowing with flame and stardust. The landscape is a surreal blend of desert, ruins, and circuitry — half mythic wasteland, half dreamcode. The tone is luminous, fierce, and sovereign. High detail, cinematic lighting, art style blending digital surrealism and visionary painting.",
